/* Genetic studies */There was no cited genetic study that supports the claims that taiwanese Chinese are related to the Ainu or the Japanese. All the major snp studies show the Taiwanese Han to be close to southern Chinese as well as a number of Taiwanese who have aboriginal admixture. But the claims that the mainstay of taiwan's population has links to Japan or the Ainu is without basis.
